``k'' commentary news file.)  
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; EUROPE &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WHAT'S SLOBODAN MILOSEVIC'S EXIT STRATEGY? &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Note 225-word optional trim at 775; 1,050 words uncut) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Moved as BC-WILL-MILOSEVIC-SURVIVE?-775&AMP;add-ECONOMIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; THE WAR MAY BE ENDING _ BUT BEWARE THE PEACE &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
