<DOCNO> NYT19990607.0013 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-07 00:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5347 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BREAKTHROUGH-KOSOVO?-     06-07 1316
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BREAKTHROUGH-KOSOVO?-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
