<P>
   MRSGORE-PROFILE _ A profile of Tipper Gore. Mrs. Gore, defined
constantly in opposition to her husband, is supposed to be the
earthy, unguarded, effervescent one. Seemingly everyone who knows
her describes her this way, and the conventional wisdom is that, in
the coming campaign, she will serve as an essential antidote to Al,
the unlabored warmth to his unyielding chill. But in a brief,
stilted conversation late last week, Mrs. Gore seemed ill prepared
for that assignment. Her answers were fuzzy, cautious, and, in a
few instances, incredible. By Frank Bruni.
