<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-07 09:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2234 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-R-DAMAGE-SUITS-REVIEW     06-07 0935
