<HEADER>
A2240 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-R-MUSEUM-BLOCKBUSTERS     06-07 0851
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-MUSEUM-BLOCKBUSTERS-REVIEW-565&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MY RENOIR BEATS YOUR VERMEER 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating) (The Week in Review) 
(lb) 
 By RALPH BLUMENTHAL   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ Summer is blockbuster season, from the multiplex to
the august halls of culture. That's one way to explain a big van
