uproar from women's groups who demanded that the pill also be
approved. The pill could be available this fall.
</P>
<P>
   _ SHERYL WuDUNN
</P>
<P>
   European Nations Vote to Become Military Power
</P>
<P>
   The European Union's 15 member nations decided to become a
