<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-07 15:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6012 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RUN-PROCHAMPIONSHIPS-     06-07 0684
