<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-07 15:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6042 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCI-STETHOSCOPE-BOS &LR;      06-07 1602
