   KOSOVO-RDP (Bonn, Germany) _ Ledeall. Daylong talks among
foreign ministers of the United States, six other Western nations
and Russia broke up Monday without Moscow's agreement on tough NATO
peace terms for Kosovo that are laid out in a draft U.N. Security
Council resolution. Developing. By Jane Perlez.
