<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   MINISTER-GAY-MARRIAGE (California) will not move in tonight's
New York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, June 7.
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
