<DOCNO> NYT19990607.0297 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-07 18:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6251 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MEANS-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      06-07 1050
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MEANS-COLUMN-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
IT'S HILLARY'S TURN 
</HEADLINE>
